00:00:23.620 --> 00:00:25.630
I know it doesn't
feel quite like it,

00:00:25.630 --> 00:00:30.220
but I would like to wish you
a belated happy [inaudible]

00:00:30.220 --> 00:00:36.010
but this event is framed
within the lecture series

00:00:36.010 --> 00:00:40.010
for [inaudible] so welcome

00:00:40.010 --> 00:00:43.600
to the African Middle
East Division,

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.850
and I'm Mary Jane Deeb.

00:00:45.850 --> 00:00:50.650
I'm the chief of the division,
