&gt;&gt; Doctor Pedram Partovi:
So we'll movie ahead

00:41:41.630 --> 00:41:44.030
and again this is another scene
where they're sort of making fun

00:41:44.030 --> 00:41:47.120
of the Hindi film,
and of the literacy,

00:41:47.120 --> 00:41:49.720
the audience's literacy,
of the Hindi film as well.

00:41:49.720 --> 00:41:52.650
So this is a scene
where again Ali,

00:41:52.650 --> 00:41:55.560
the character we just saw
jumping around in the pool,

00:41:55.560 --> 00:41:58.070
is dressed up now
as an Indian price.

00:41:58.070 --> 00:42:01.900
Or he looks more like
