00:42:01.900 --> 00:42:05.320
And he's again --
His comic sidekick,

00:42:05.320 --> 00:42:06.620
we've seen this guy before.

00:42:06.620 --> 00:42:08.390
This is Taghi Zohoori dressed

00:42:08.390 --> 00:42:10.850
up like a British
