00:42:14.610 --> 00:42:16.930
of the girl that we just saw.

00:42:16.930 --> 00:42:19.280
And he's going to try
to pull off the fact

00:42:19.280 --> 00:42:22.550
that he's an Indian prince,
and he's going to do it by sort

00:42:22.550 --> 00:42:25.710
of pretending to
speak the language

00:42:25.710 --> 00:42:28.210
of the Hindi film, essentially.

